I have a great way to make money, read on. The game does get boring once you buy all the add ons but the game play is still neat since they will sustain themselves while you are away. As long as they have food and you've visited them/praised them it will be fine. Now to make money, adopt a person that makes a really low income to start (those are the ones that make the most in the end). Make them work and praise them repetitively. They will try and run away by the third praise but just drag them back and keep doing it for about 10 times. exit the game and make sure it has stopped running in the background. Go to the settings in your phone and change the time to 5 hours ahead or one day ahead. Check your game and they will have made much more money. Change the time back on your phone. You can do this three or 4 times every day but keep in mind that although you make quick money, your people will age faster! No biggie if you want to see more generations. Good game!
